products.title: Light Blue Aluminium Venetian
products.description: The light blue aluminium venetian blind is a gentle balance between a soft pastel tone, and a stronger sky blue hue. This is ideal for areas of your home where you want to inject some colour, but without it dominating the space. Keep your blinds looking their best with their easy to wipe clean aluminium slats, just use a damp cloth to wipe away any dirt or stains. Raise and lower your blind to the perfect height, and then angle the venetian slats to control the light entering your home.
